  <brief_title>HIV Testing and Brief Alcohol Intervention for Young Drinkers in the Emergency Department</brief_title>
  <official_title>Addressing HIV Risk in Young Unhealthy Alcohol Drinkers in the Emergency Department With Rapid HIV Testing and Brief Intervention</official_title>
  <sponsors>
